RACE.RACE_TEXT: WYOMING DOWNS RACE 6 5F Dirt CR: 72. Allowance Purse 8000. FOR FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON TWO RACES. Three Year Olds, 124 lbs.; Older, 126 lbs. (If Race Fails To Fill With Six Or More Accredited Wyoming Breds, It Will Be Taken Open).
RACE.FOOTNOTES: COME CORRECT stalked WAPITI ROSE and THIRSTY NO MORE, ran the rail the whole race had a final drive at the sixteenth pole to win. WAPITI ROSE set the pace early ran the two wide got caught at the sixteenth pole just missed the win. IMAMONEYMAKER ran off pace from pack leaders went into the turn four wide came out of the turn seven wide. THIRSTY NO MORE broke out first off pace from WAPITI ROSE went three wide into the turn and faded at the sixteenth pole. SATIN HEART ran six wide the whole race, came out of the turn eight wide with no final kick. SOUTHRN SWEETHEART ran the rail the whole race with no menace trailed the pack. PER RULING #23-0048 FROM THE WYOMING GAMING COMMISSION, COME CORRECT WAS DISQUALIFIED FROM 1st TO UNPLACED DUE TO A POSITIVE TEST.
